+Here is a **detailed, production-ready English prompt** for the *Celestial Keysmith* concept — suitable for game design docs, prototype generation, or AI-assisted development:
+
+---
+
+## **✨ Celestial Keysmith – Detailed Game Concept Prompt (English)**
+
+**Title:** *Celestial Keysmith*
+**Theme:** Cosmic Blacksmithing / Astral Crafting
+**Core Loop:** Collect ➝ Craft Keys ➝ Solve Vault Puzzles ➝ Leave Clues ➝ Explore
+
+---
+
+### **🔑 High-Level Description**
+
+Design a game called **Celestial Keysmith**, where the player becomes an astral blacksmith who forges magical keys from “stardust alloys” and uses them to open **Celestial Vaults**—mysterious puzzle chambers floating in the cosmos. Each vault contains **clues left by other players**, creating asynchronous multiplayer exploration and discovery.
+
+---
+
+### **🌠 Worldbuilding & Aesthetic Direction**
+
+* Set in a shimmering astral realm full of floating islands, nebula forges, energy rivers, and ancient constellations.
+* Visual tone: “Astral artisan shop” + “mystical cosmic ruins.”
+* Color palette: deep cosmos blues, gold glows, prismatic stardust, neon accents.
+* Sound design: metallic chimes, echoing cosmic winds, soft resonant forging impacts, faint whispers of distant stars.
+
+---
+
+### **🔨 Core Gameplay Systems**
+
+#### **1. Stardust Collection**
+
+* Player travels to cosmic zones (Meteor Gardens, Nebula Mines, Comet Trails).
+* Collects raw materials:
+
+  * **Star Iron**
+  * **Nebula Quartz**
+  * **Void Glass**
+  * **Aurora Threads**
+* Resources have rarity and elemental affinities (solar, lunar, void, storm).
+
+#### **2. Key Forging (Crafting System)**
+
+* Craft keys using a multi-step forging mechanic:
+
+  1. Smelt materials at the **Astral Forge**.
+  2. Shape the key with celestial molds.
+  3. Imbue magic through constellation patterns.
+* Keys have stats:
+
+  * **Alignment** (solar/lunar/void)
+  * **Complexity** (basic / ornate / legendary)
+  * **Attunement** (puzzle type unlocked)
+
+#### **3. Celestial Vaults (Puzzle Rooms)**
+
+Every vault is a self-contained challenge. Types include:
+
+* **Constellation Logic Puzzles** – rotate star nodes to form required shapes.
+* **Runic Lock Patterns** – align glyphs based on cryptic hints.
+* **Astral Mechanisms** – move floating platforms, redirect starlight beams.
+* **Temporal Gates** – time-based puzzles where cosmic currents shift.
+
+Vault difficulties scale with the **complexity of the key** used.
+
+#### **4. Player-Generated Clues**
+
+* Each vault contains clues left by previous players:
+
+  * Notes, sketches, constellation outlines, fragment messages, hints.
+* System ensures:
+
+  * Useful clues are surfaced to new players
+  * Troll/low-quality clues are filtered via community rating
+  * Clues have visual styles tied to the leaving player’s forge aesthetic
+
+#### **5. Asynchronous Multiplayer Discovery**
+
+* When players complete a vault:
+
+  * They may leave behind a clue
+  * They unlock someone else’s clue chain
+* Vaults evolve based on community-driven puzzle paths.
+
+---
+
+### **🌀 Progression System**
+
+#### **Keysmith Level**
+
+* XP from:
+
+  * Forging keys
+  * Opening vaults
+  * Leaving highly-rated clues
+* Unlocks new crafting recipes, improved forge tools, advanced materials.
+
+#### **Cosmic Zones Progression**
+
+Players unlock deeper layers of the astral world:
+
+1. **Beginner Zone: Luminous Workshop**
+2. **Starbreaker Isles**
+3. **The Nebula Maze**
+4. **The Void Spiral**
+5. **The Celestial Apex**
+
+---
+
+### **🎯 Player Motivations**
+
+* Creative crafting and experimentation
+* Solving intelligent puzzle challenges
+* Discovering community-written secrets
+* Progression of the forge and skills
+* Exploring visually beautiful cosmic realms
+
+---
+
+### **🪐 Meta Systems**
+
+* Daily/Weekly “Cosmic Currents” that alter puzzle modifiers
+* Seasonal events (Meteor Showers, Eclipse Season, Comet Bloom)
+* Cosmetic unlocks for forge tools & key shapes
+* Collections: “Vault Almanac,” “Constellation Codex,” “Stardust Bestiary”
+
+---
+
+### **📦 Output Requirements (if used for AI generation)**
+
+When generating content for this prompt, produce:
+
+* Detailed mechanics
+* UI mockups
+* Crafting recipes
+* Sample vault puzzles
+* Visual concept descriptions
+* Narrative lore fragments
+* Player progression charts
+
+Tone: Epic, mystical, cosmic craftsmanship with puzzle exploration.
+
+---
+
+If you want, I can also generate:
+🔸 *Game design doc (GDD)*
+🔸 *Pitch deck*
+🔸 *Lore bible*
+🔸 *Sample puzzles & blueprints*
+🔸 *Monetization model*
+🔸 *Farcaster Frame version for interactive play*
+
+Just tell me!
+
+```
+
+Generate an app logo and update the app metadata title and description.

